rows.label: qst500205_msg0001
rows.name:
Meh-meh-meh?! Foorara knew
friends would find Foorara!

rows.label: qst500205_msg0002
rows.name:
Foorara wanted to meet nice Emperor,
so went into throne room with no
permission, but got chased by soldiers!

rows.label: qst500205_msg0004
rows.name:
Had enough of being chased though.
Foorara want to go back to Invidia cave
and snuggle up eating mushrooms...

rows.label: qst500205_msg0005
rows.name:
But Voltis Trade Guild Walky-Walky
Guide Book say, Walky-Walky Nopon
must not go to same place twice!

rows.label: qst500205_msg0006
rows.name:
Is sad, but Foorara have to look for
different cave to snuggle up instead.

rows.label: qst500205_msg0007
rows.name:
Anyway, maybe we meet again.
Best of luck!
